ntation at a dod training day said the review found the navy not in full compliance with federal policies on human subjects protection it was pointed out that the navy had no single point of accountability for human subject protections in  he became under secretary of the air force thus serving as department of defense executive agent and milestone decision authority for space starting in  he worked at the colorado state university where sega has served as vice president of energy and the environment for the colorado state university research foundation a private nonprofit advocacy organization for the university and as the woodward professor of systems engineering in the college of engineering in september  colorado state university and the ohio state university collaborated to create a shared position called the vice president and enterprise executive for energy and the environment in this position sega will help the institutions work together to identify and lead potential national initiatives and economic development opportunities and will also look for opportunities for collaboration between the universities awards and honorsedit distinguished graduate of the united states air force academy  top graduate of the pilot instructor training course  officer of the year in the department of physics us air force academy  meritorious service medal commendation medal usaf reserve achievement medal air force research fellow — air force office of scientific research  received the outstanding faculty award — department of electrical engineering at the university of colorado  selected to the academic hall of fame of his high school in macedonia ohio  reserve officer of the year ima air force space command  reserve officer of the year ima us air force  received an honorary doctorate from clarkson university  nasa space flight medals  and  nasa superior achievement award  nasa director of operations russia  nasa outstanding leadership medal  colorado space hall of fame on  oc